In order to execute the method, select a '''Ship instance''' and invoke {{MenuCommand|Resistance → [[Image:Resistance_BlountFox.svg|16px]] Resistance Blount and Fox prediction}}. 

The ship data will be obtain from the ship and the user only needs to enter the boundary conditions.
Data obtained from the vessel can be edited.


